reviewText:
no very interesting, seemed to be just threw together,
i did not get the true feel for game day.
 in my opionon just a quick way to make a buck for who ever put out this video. no way would i recomend this.

If you are even a stay at home on the couch fan of the Auburn University Tigers this video will make your hairs stand on end.  I could smell the concession stand through my TV, hear the Bodda Getta chant, and lost my breath with the segment on War Eagle.  If you know and love Auburn you have to have this DVD.
